Connect local microphone into the audio output of a remote machine:
cat /dev/audio | ssh user@machine 'dd bs=1k of=/dev/dsp'
If that doesn't work try "of=/dev/audio" instead of "of=/dev/dsp"
For the reverse effect try the following command:
ssh user@machine 'dd bs=1k if=/dev/audio' > /dev/audio
